see what indices do i have 

curl 'localhost:9200/_cat/indices?v'


Delete index
with kibana console 
    DELETE /twitter


Elastic can be configurate to throw out some of the terms for example stop words


The REST endpoint is /{index}/_close and /{index}/_open. For example:

curl -XPOST 'localhost:9200/my_index/_close'

curl -XPOST 'localhost:9200/my_index/_open'

Settings

curl -XGET 'http://localhost:9200/wazzup/_settings'



